data.description: VA assumable, ask for details - seller offering up to $10k for interest rate buydown which can significantly reduce monthly payments as determined by lender - step inside to the open-concept living area that boasts an abundance of natural light, complete with remote controlled electric screens - the gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless appliances, custom cabinets, a huge center island, & a walk-in pantry - the luxurious primary suite, a true sanctuary for relaxation, features a generously sized bedroom, a walk-in closet, & a spa-like ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub, a separate shower, & double vanities - two guest bedrooms with a shared full bath complete the first floor - upstairs you'll find an additional spacious guest bedroom, full bath, & either a large 5th bedroom or bonus room - the outdoor living space is equally impressive with the expansive patio, where you can enjoy al fresco dining, entertain guests, or simply unwind - schedule your private tour today!
